highlights.text: Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Kochi. “Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” is the highest at #2.
“Dreamers [Music from the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 Official Soundtrack]” by Jung Kook, BTS, and FIFA Sound is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kochi at #58.
“Aise Kyun - Ghazal Version” by Rekha Bhardwaj, Anurag Saikia, Raj Shekhar, and Mismatched - Cast is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kochi, up 36 spots at #56.
“Munbe Vaa” by A.R. Rahman, Shreya Ghoshal, and Naresh Iyer has been on Top Songs Kochi the longest, at 58 weeks straight.
